”>;“辅助功能”>;“触摸”，然后打开“辅助触摸”。单击“双击”并自定义该设置以截取屏幕截图。然后，屏幕右侧将出现一个虚拟主页按钮。快速点击该按钮两次即可截取屏幕截图。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f0be2640-42a3-11ee-bdf3-cc1cad664e38" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f0be2640-42a3-11ee-bdf3-cc1cad664e38" style="height:1700px;width:2500px;" alt="如何在 iPad 上截取屏幕截图" data-uuid="84833781-daa6-34af-8f5f-0d49766f08d9"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">朱莉娅·梅尔卡多 / Engadget 摄</div></figure><h2>Apple Pencil 用户的奖励</h2><p>使用 Apple Pencil 从屏幕左下角向上滑动即可截取屏幕截图。编辑菜单将自动打开，从那里，您可以使用铅笔使用多个画笔选项对图像进行注释和标记。点击完成并保存以完成编辑。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/how-to-take-a-screenshot-on-ipad-120059001.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/how-to-take-a-screenshot-on-ipad-120059001.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ab14c461-dd42-4774-9a7d-8884ca23d3b2</guid><dc:creator>朱莉娅·梅尔卡多</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 12:00:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693311505</ingested><modified> 2023-08-29T12:18:32+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Julia Mercado]]></category><media:content height="1600" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/237f0220-42a4-11ee-afff-9cb60e57e2c5" width="2400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></medi